name: Phyta_I
description:
Phyta_I is part of the Micrographia series that takes inspiration from the early explorers of the microscopic world. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 3505X5250px PNG [bitmap image]
2021 | Mark Webster @motiondesign_01
